title: Promise
subTitle: A retired Union contract scout embarks on a deadly mission to find out what happened to his true love and her little girl.

title: 48 Hours and 1 Minute
subTitle: When the 48-hour law prevents police from searching for an abducted child, a resilient mother is forced to hunt through the perilous streets of Belgrade, despite the effects of her psychiatric medication.

subTitle: Unsettling hospitality, odd rules and unexplained occurrences turn a getaway at a lake house for friends and family into a vacation from hell.

subTitle: Abby and her estranged father fight to survive after being stranded on a remote mountainside.

subTitle: Two outlaws in the 1880s take up a lucrative assignment that lands them in the jaws of danger. Only time can tell if they will make it or get slaughtered.
